---

<SEMLayout title="Your Partner in Success">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <SEMHero
    label="YOUR PARTNER IN SUCCESS"
    title="Focus on your business, leave the marketing to us"
    highlight="marketing"
  >
    <div slot="image" class="relative h-[400px] md:h-[500px] w-full overflow-hidden">
      <img
        src="/images/hero/hero-v3.jpg"
        alt="Sharp End Marketing - creative storytelling"
        class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20" />
    </div>
  </SEMHero>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <SEMSectionHeader
        label="OUR SERVICES"
        icon="brush"
        title="Digital Marketing & Social Media."
      />
      <p class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-4xl text-center text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        We provide a full suite of digital marketing & social media services. Complimenting our marketing menu is website design and content creation, these are foundational pieces that round out our creative service offerings. Well....let's not forget good storytelling, because without that, the rest doesn't really matter. We excel at building great storylines that will attract your ideal audience. Artificial Intelligence (AI) surrounds all of us today. At Sharp End Marketing we have embraced this revolution. Let us show your team how to harness the value of AI for specific tasks. Click on the numbered tiles for details or better yet, <a href="/contact" class="font-medium text-teal-solid hover:underline">reach out today</a> to see if your eligible for our no-obligation mini audit of your website and social media.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4">
        {services.map(service => (
          <SEMServiceCard {...service} />
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Sharp End -->
  <section class="bg-bg-light px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="grid items-start gap-12 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="section-label mb-4">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z" />
            </svg>
            WHY SHARP END?
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-medium text-heading">Where Storytelling is Central</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
            At Sharp End Marketing our goal is to help our clients connect with their target audience in a meaningful way highlighting their unique value propositions thus creating a reason for that audience to engage.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
            We believe marketing starts with strategy & finishes with storytelling. We're eager to hear your unique story so we can build a winning strategy, then weave storytelling into all aspects of your marketing to help you reach your business goals. Leave the marketing to us, when you get to focus on building your business, good things happen.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white p-12 shadow-card">
          <p class="font-accent text-h3 text-center text-text-muted leading-snug">
            Focus on building your business. Leave the marketing to us.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Process -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <SEMSectionHeader
        label="OUR PROCESS"
        icon="route"
        title="We're Big on Keeping it Simple!"
        subtitle="There is no magic here, just a well thought out plan, hard work and a dash of luck. Marketing isn't an exact science but we've distilled it down to our formula, here's how we do it:"
      />
      <div class="mt-12 grid items-start gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
          <img
            src="/images/process/our-process.png"
            alt="Sharp End Marketing process: Discover, Create, Analyze"
            class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-10">
          {processSteps.map(step => (
            <SEMProcessStep {...step} />
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Success Stories -->
  <section class="bg-bg-light px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <SEMSectionHeader
        label="SUCCESS STORIES"
        icon="trophy"
        title="Transforming brands, one project at a time"
        subtitle="See how we've transformed brands and driven results."
      />
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        {caseStudies.map(study => (
          <SEMCaseStudyCard {...study} />
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Blog / Insights -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <SEMSectionHeader
        label="LATEST INSIGHTS"
        icon="search"
        title="Insights & Inspiration"
        subtitle="Stay ahead with the latest marketing trends."
      />
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        {blogPosts.map((post, i) => (
          <SEMBlogCard {...post} featured={i === 0} />
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <SEMCTASection
    title="Ready to Elevate Your Brand?"
    description="Partner with Sharp End and let's create something extraordinary together."
    ctaText="Get in Touch"
    ctaHref="/contact"
  >
    <img
      slot="image"
      src="/images/cta/cta-img.avif"
      alt="Sharp End Marketing creative work"
      class="h-auto max-h-80 w-auto rounded-xl object-contain"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </SEMCTASection>
</SEMLayout>
